descriptionHTML:
Travel throught the hyperspace just to land in our new awesome Tatooine Star Wars Watchface, inspired on Star Wars universe. Get inside the luke skin in their war against the empire, go far far away with the speeder and get lost in the horizon.


How to use it:
- The two suns show the time
- White sun point the hours
- Orange sun point the minutes
- You can tap on screen to show help numbers or hide them
- On dimmed screen numbers are always shown

Features:
- Interactive mode enabled, show hours help on tap, the two suns of Tatooine Watch Face show the current time, white sun for hours and orange sun for minutes.
- Dimmed screen animation, smoth animation on dimmed screen transition, the same effects used in the films, it works like a charm!
- Beautiful svg landscape and speeder illustration
- Speeder floating animation
- More features will be updated soon...

Supported for Android Wear Devices:
Tatooine Watch Face supports all Android Wear devices, if you have questions in a specific device.

The latest version of Android Wear is required for Interactive Mode.

Permissions:

- No permission is required
